txt.en: Breach in the Darkness: The Invaders

'The Withered Tree has let a raiding party of Orcs into the Cisterns. I can hear their evil speech echoing throughout the tunnels and caverns. It won't be long until they've made their way to the surface and start attacking Gondor!'
Orcs can be found throughout the Cisterns.\n\nYou should defeat Orcs in the Cisterns.
Orcs have invaded the Cisterns and it is up to you to defeat the raiding party.
